<title>COME, THOU FOUNT OF EVERY BLESSING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hungin, vangsakna cheng Tuikhuk,
 Ka lung pakla sak sakin;
 Zahngaihna lui luong kang ngeilo,
 Pakla ngeih sa di'n a sam.
 La ngaihnawp um chuh ei hilh in,
 Van mite'n a sak u chuh;
 Pakcha'ng ka ka lunga cham zing,
 Nei hehpih zieka tatna.

[V2]
 2. Ebenezer zie'n dawh khang ka,
 Nei panpihna'n ka hung hi;
 Na phasakna ziek ka kinem,
 Bittaka In hung tun ding.
 Ka man laiin Isun ei hawl,
 Pathien huong apat taimang;
 Lauhum apat ei hukdawk di'n,
 A thisan lul A pie tai.

[V3]
 3. Na zangaihna leiba ka hi,
 Nicheng in ka hih ka he'i;
 Zahngaih na'n, Lalpa dettak in,
 Ka lunggil vakvai kanin.
 Vakvai ka hi, Lalpa, ka he'i,
 Ka hehpih Pathien nusie'n;
 Ka lunggil lan la, tiemteh in,
 Tiemteh in, chunglam thil in.</lyrics>
</song>